# Node Components

Every node runs three, in coordination.

## kubelet — the node agent

> **Not a Pod** — a **systemd service.**

1. Register the node
2. Watch Pods bound here (`spec.nodeName`)
3. Drive runtime: pull · netns · mount · start
4. Probes · restart per policy
5. Report status · **evict** on pressure

> **Doesn't schedule** — runs what's **bound** to it.

## kube-proxy

> Service data plane — programs `iptables`/`IPVS`/`nftables`. DaemonSet. **Optional** (Cilium eBPF replaces).

## Container runtime

> K8s ships none — speaks **CRI** to **containerd** (common) or **CRI-O**. Docker's `dockershim` **removed in 1.24**. Socket: `/run/containerd/containerd.sock`.

> = the **Node runtime** box — the *execute* half.
